<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <title>New Area Reservation - NeighbourHub</title>
  <style type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" media="all">
    body {
      width: 100% !important;
      height: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.4;
      background-color: #f5f7f9;
      color: #1b3b4c;
      font-family: Arial, 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #3e94bf;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    p {
      color: #1b3b4c;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f5f7f9;
      padding: 20px 0;
    }

    .email-content {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #a8b9c1;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-radius: 6px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #3e94bf;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .email-header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: white;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #6e8793;
    }

    .button {
      background-color: #62b3d8;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-content">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>NeighbourHub</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <h1>Nova Reserva Criada</h1>
        <p>Olá,</p>
        <p>Uma nova reserva foi submetida na plataforma <strong>NeighbourHub</strong> para o condomínio <strong>{{condominiumName}}</strong>.</p>
        <p><strong>Utilizador:</strong> {{userName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Data incio:</strong> {{startDate}}</p>
        <p><strong>Data fim:</strong> {{endDate}}</p>
        <p><strong>Espaço solicitado:</strong> {{commonArea}}</p>

        <a href="{{adminPanelUrl}}" class="button">Ver reserva</a>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        Este é um e-mail automático enviado pela plataforma NeighbourHub.<br />
        Não respondas diretamente a este e-mail.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
